Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:04.00,Memory,,0,0,0,,Fujiwarano Sai, a go player from the Heian period...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:08.50,Memory,,0,0,0,,has passed through time and returned to\Nthe world in the mind of Shindou Hikaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.38,0:00:11.70,Memory,,0,0,0,,in order to obtain the Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:46.09,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(375,115)}The Twenty-Seventh Match
