Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:52.18,Note,,0,0,10,,{\fs19\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}S\Nh\Ni\Nn\Nd\No\Nu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning every game is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:02:02.52,Sai,,0,0,0,,Of course it is. You are playing\Nagainst those who are well aware of\Ntheir goals and walking towards it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The next study session with\Nmy master is on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, you went to Mr. Morishita's study session?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.28,0:02:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it helped him a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should join a study session too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.95,0:02:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But playing go all day long and all night long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, we need to let lose sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wanna, go do karaoke\Non our way home tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's! Wanna go bowling afterwards too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Isumi-kun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll call home then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:02.25,Note,,0,0,60,,{\fs45\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Haze Public Junior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:00.66,Background,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.08,Background,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do Karaoke or go bowling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to play at the Go club sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do after I go here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You always go home right after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You study Go at home everyday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:02.50,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yup! I teach him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou don't teach me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. What\Nabout the tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls are going, right? It's almost time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that response?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mitani? Did he quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried calling him a few times...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely even talk to him now\Nbecause I'm in a separate class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't bring up the Go club anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he comes back someday too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.50,Sai,,0,0,0,,Seems like it's become lonely here at the Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Want me to play you guys for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be bored playing you\Ntwo crappy girls all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play all three of you at\Nthe same time! Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't come anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume-kun and I were just talking about\Nit... Mitani-kun might come back eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he comes to take a look...\Nif Hikaru was having fun here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun wouldn't like it...\NHe wouldn't come anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:08.74,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just once won't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get another Go board, I'll play you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:19.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,Wasabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You two place all the stones you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that little of us!? I'm really\Ngoing to place all the stones I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.92,Background,,0,0,0,,How's this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that? Are you sure it's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this!? But there's so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I'm getting nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(263,77)}Chemistry Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... Hikaru wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! I'm so angry! I placed so many stones too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He just keeps taking them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you're not holding back at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always doing that to me. I've\Ngot to let the stress out somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mitani!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru just dropped by today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care whether Shindou's here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my chemistry book,\Nso I came to get it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just get it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.38,Background,,0,0,0,,You must be happy, getting\Nlessons from the spectacular Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,About you forgetting your\Nchemistry book... is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The rearmost desk by the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.55,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(391,186)}Chemistry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.55,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373,390)}Mitani Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing. Mitani-kun forgot his\NChemistry book, so he came to get it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he had Chemistry today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamako-sensei wasn't here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.64,Background,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Mitani-kun's never going to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean up the stones already and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I won't come anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\move(298,451,298,19)\iclip(95,436,500,480)}Come on to the Basketball Club!!
