Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.33,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(416,56)}G\NO\N\NC\NL\NU\NB\N\NR\NE\NC\NR\NU\NI\NT\NI\NN\NG
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.33,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs16\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(516,244}B\NE\NG\NI\NN\NN\NE\NR\NS\N\NA\NR\NE\N\NW\NE\NL\NC\NO\NM\NE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.33,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fs17.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\frz0\pos(320,445)}We're at the Chemistry Lab afterschool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly a year ago wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shindou pulled me into the Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.75,Background,,0,0,0,,We put up a poster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one's coming... not even one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun won't come back either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make another poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun came last year\Nwhen we made a new poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, you girls have to practice\Nfor the tournament next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Are we really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going. I already asked the\Ngirl from the Volleyball club. So we\Nhave three including you, Kumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could go too, but I'm the only guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.89,Background,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... ahh... I came to join the Go club... may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.87,Background,,0,0,0,,I heard we're having a quiz today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.46,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... is Mitani-kun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you Natsume. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the Go club...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Against those two girls that\Ndon't know how to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They know how to play now! They're\Nstarting to learn how to play a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not what I'm here\Nfor. We got a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That seventh grader isn't strong or\Nanything, but he's about as good as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we have two male members now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you come back we can go to the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you play first board, Mitani-kun!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You there. The bell's rung,\Ngo back to your own class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me after school. I'll come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:29.88,Background,,0,0,0,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.22,Background,,0,0,0,,Well, to begin with, in yesterday's homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:42.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(263,77)}Chemistry Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're doing the lab\Non page 47 of your textbook,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.33,Background,,0,0,0,,so each group is to get whatever you need for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.19,Background,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.88,Background,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me! He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.34,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll clean that up so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(368,230)}Fujisaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.80,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(440,230)}Akari
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Match records? They keep this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:35.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Man they play a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Five books in total?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh so they have five whole members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The girls that don't know how to play and Natsume and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Koike Hitoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.18,Thinking,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.12,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(302,281)}Mitani Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.15,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey Mitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing! Help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Natsume-kun you gave up after that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll try asking him again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go again too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure something good'll happen\Nif we just keep on trying, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, Koike-kun's in the Go club now too so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Is that the new poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.93,Background,,0,0,0,,I thought about putting a Tsumego in but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.34,Background,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's great! It's very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.62,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mitani-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going with us to the tournament!?\NYou're going to play first board for us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!? Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.49,Background,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.26,Background,,0,0,0,,then, you came here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.89,Background,,0,0,0,,to play us every now and then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:28.30,Note,,0,0,0,,[loae666: MWAHAHAHAHA You have fallen into\Ntheir trap! You have taken a step down a very\Nslippery slope! Within the next 25 episodes, you WILL\Nbe playing in the tournament! MWAHAHAHAHA]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.36,Background,,0,0,0,,We've got to get another board!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:28.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Umm, can you play both Natsume-kun\Nand Koishi-kun to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Koike from the seventh\Ngrade. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Play us after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to show him how much better we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:42.27,Background,,0,0,0,,Waaasssuuuppp?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.00,Background,,0,0,0,,Kaneko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get some practice and drink some\Nbuds. We are going to a tournament after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should come here as much\Nas possible and get some practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who's the best player here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Nigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really confident. You're\Ngoing to play me evenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our first match. We have to play evenly to\Nsee how strong we are relative to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But go ahead and put some\Nstones down if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me? Play with a handicap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh so you are confident. Then let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm first, You're at a disadvantage,\Nso wanna tack on 10.5 moku komi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.54,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Komi is usually 5.5, she's making fun of Mitani here]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god please! Don't let Mitani-kun leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, I'm a little rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Kaneko-san's stones connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:16.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,No. Mitani-kun knows that he's at an\Nadvantage, so he didn't try to forcefully\Nkill them, and let them connect, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:26.61,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But Kaneko-san is a lot stronger than either I\Nor Koike-kun. No wonder she was so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,About time you resigned, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... you're rather strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the "I resign?" the "I resign?".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are opponents that\Nyou really don't want to resign to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But that won't work. "I resign"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a 3 stone handicap from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you can win at 3 stones, just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:03.03,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, those words are going to hurt when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! We've got to record this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally starting to fill in Mitani-kun's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't record a game like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.64,Background,,0,0,0,,We've got to make a book for Kaneko-san too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it! Make it! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:26.48,Background,,0,0,0,,I have to record my increasing wins and\Ndecreasing handicap against this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.58,Background,,0,0,0,,Thanks Kaneko-san! It was fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Kaneko-san, you're in the\Nsame class as Hikaru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Could you tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That Mitani-kun's started\Nto show up at the Go club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To stop worrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. But Shindou's going to be absent\Ntomorrow, so I'll tell him on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Absent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:20:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he told the teacher something about\Ngoing to a Wakajishisen or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wakajishisen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has his own\Ntournaments. Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,G..Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.78,Background,,0,0,0,,We're playing at three stones tomorrow too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I was coming tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll make sure to mark\Ndown your loss by default.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is it three stones!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost every game today at three stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it four stones if I lose\Nevery game tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said! Who said I was coming tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.79,0:22:12.32,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord3\1c&H0E00DC&\3c&H3AFF00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\pos(172,355)}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.32,NoteArialEF,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord3\1c&H0E00DC&\3c&H3AFF00&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\pos(298,355)}Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(471,355)}Igo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(247.625,171.25)}Umezawa Yukari's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do "Fuseki" today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&H177AF8&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(320,338)}Teacher Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs19\1c&H008E05&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(594,167)}T\NO\ND\NA\NY\N\NW\NE\N\NA\NR\NE\N\ND\NO\NI\NN\NG
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.34,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs19\1c&H1300EA&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(487,337)}F\NU\NS\NE\NK\NI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuseki is the first stage of a game of Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:20.16,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\1c&H018C09&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(162,277)}[Fuseki] is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:20.16,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\1c&H018C09&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(315,359)}the placement of the first stones, and is important!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:22.48,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Loae is horrible at this >_< I'm maybe about 10k\Nin strength in the early game. I make up for it in the mid\Ngame though, and I'm horrible at the end game >_<]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:22.17,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&HFC0003&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(280,415)}Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:23.73,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&HFB24F1&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(318,410)}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:30.31,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&HFA0002&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(320,31)}This is my territory\Nover here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.34,0:22:30.31,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&HA059E9&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(320,236)}This side is\Nmy territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.17,0:22:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You start declaring which areas you\Nwant to make your own territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.21,0:22:33.79,Note,,0,0,15,,{\an2\fs30\1c&H058C0B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1}If you move on further...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In this were to happen, this area\Nmight become black's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This area here may become white's territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.43,0:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Black's territory looks larger, so\Nlet's say that white moves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When this happens, the Fuseki\Nis over and a fight begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:54.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&H028D0B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(320,297)}[Fuseki] has no set rules
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:54.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&H028D0B&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\pos(320,360)}So think about different ways of playing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to play the "Fuseki" portion while\Ntrying to maintain a balance with your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.37,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\1c&H0F00EF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad1\i1\pos(320,303)}To be continued...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:23:03.36,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad0\pos(320,44)}The Ninth Wakajishisen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Mashiba-san would be a little better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which one's the pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! Beating me at a place like this is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worthless unless you pass the pro exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you! Mashiba!
